<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26> a ns1:CourseGuide ;
    ns1:hasCompetency <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/CO3>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/CP1>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/CP2>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/CP4>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/CP6>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/HA1>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/HA4> ;
    ns1:hasDidacticResource <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/1>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/2>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/3>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/4>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/5>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/6> ;
    ns1:hasEvaluation <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/evaluation> ;
    ns1:hasLearningResult <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/RA1>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/RA2> ;
    ns1:hasSyllabus <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/syllabus> ;
    ns1:inpersonHours "68 horas (43.6%)"@es ;
    ns1:numberOfCredits 6.0 ;
    ns1:otherInformation """The course will be taught in English.

Besides the use of the Moodle platform, in case of need, the communication between professors and students will be carried out using Zoom.

The answers of the tests questions will not be published since each student answers different ones, randomly drawn from a pool of questions.
In this course, collaboration is encouraged, but in no way copying. Copying laboratories is considered academic fraud, which represents a serious infraction contemplated in the Learning Assessment Regulations of the Universidad Politécnica de Madrid. Also, the use of AI tools is prohibited and may lead to a disciplinary action. In that sense, any evaluation or submission is open to require a supplementary oral assessment by the teacher to validate that it has been made by the student without the help of AI systems.


Relationship with Sustainable Development Goals:

On the one hand, the course contributes to SDG 4 (sub-objetive 4.4): Increase the number of young and adult people having professional and technical competences necessary to have access to employment and entrepreneurship.

On the other hand, the course studies fundamental mathematical and statistical tools to be employed in the modelling of different types of systems such as biological ones (SDG 3), data processing ones for industrial innovation and sustainable cities/communities (SDGs 9 and 11), climate ones (SDG 13) or ecosystems (SDGs 14 and 15).
In the course, collaboration is encouraged, but in no way copying. Copying laboratories is considered academic fraud, which represents a serious infraction contemplated in the Learning Assessment Regulations of the Universidad Politécnica de Madrid."""@es ;
    ns1:periodEndingMonth "Enero"@es ;
    ns1:periodStartingMonth "Septiembre"@es ;
    ns1:teachingPeriod "2025-26" ;
    ns1:teachingPeriodMonths "Septiembre-Enero"@es ;
    ns1:totalHours "68 horas"@es ;
    schema:activitiesWorkload "100%"@es ;
    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """Machine learning is a discipline that provides a body of knowledge and associated modeling techniques to solve scientific and engineering problems (aimed to describe, predict or explain), in which we have data or experimental knowledge as a main resource.
This course covers the characterization of the basic types of learning problems and the study of the fundamental modelling paradigms aimed to solve them. To strengthen the understanding of the field of machine learning, the course follows a practical approach where the application of fundamental concepts and techniques is central to the development of the syllabus.

Students taking this course will learn to implement models and their respective evaluation in real-case scenarios using Python and its ecosystem of libraries and tools."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/pedro.zufiria%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/o.araque%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/pedro.zufiria%40upm.es> ;
    schema:name "Machine Learning: Models And Applications"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/CO3> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CO3" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Conocer diversas aplicaciones de las teorías matemáticas y su modelización en otros entornos o disciplinas que permitan adaptar los conocimientos matemáticos a nuevos problemas.TIPO: Conocimientos o contenidos/ To understand various applications of mathematical theories and their modeling in different contexts or disciplines, allowing the adaptation of mathematical knowledge to new problems. Type: Knowledge"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/CP1> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CP1" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Utilizar programas informáticos especializados como laboratorio para diseñar, construir o validar hipótesis científicas en.alguno de los ámbitos de las matemáticas. TIPO: Competencias."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/CP2> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CP2" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Ser capaz de trabajar en equipos multidisciplinares que involucren conocimientos matemáticos avanzados en áreas teóricas o aplicadas.TIPO: Competencias."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/CP4> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CP4" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Comunicar de forma oral y escrita conocimientos y conclusiones científicas, valorando diferentes interpretaciones en públicos especializados y no especializados de una manera clara y rigurosa. TIPO: Competencias"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/CP6> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CP6" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Reflexionar sobre la relevancia social y ética de la aplicación de los conocimientos adquiridos a determinados problemas.TIPO: Competencias"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/HA1> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "HA1" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Aplicar los conocimientos matemáticos adquiridos a la resolución de problemas nuevos de una manera crítica, generando hipótesis de trabajo claras, definiciones precisas, nuevos enfoques con fundamento matemático y soluciones originales. TIPO: Habilidades o destrezas/ To apply acquired mathematical knowledge to solving new problems critically, generating clear working hypotheses, precise definitions, new mathematically grounded approaches, and original solutions.Type: Skills"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/HA4> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "HA4" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Poseer destreza para proponer, validar e interpretar modelos matemáticos de diferente dificultad en situaciones reales complejas, utilizando las herramientas matemáticas más adecuadas a los fines que se persigan, y valorando las hipótesis y conclusiones asociadas a cada nivel de dificultad del modelo. TIPO: Habilidades o destrezas"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/RA1> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA1" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "To understand and apply the fundamental models in unsupervised, supervised, and reinforcement learning problems."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/RA2> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA2" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Los resultados de aprendizaje en las tres categorías propuestas: conocimientos/contenidos, habilidades y competencias son los señalados en la memoria del título"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/1> a ns1:DidacticResource ;
    ns1:bibliographyDescription "It addresses machine learning based on probablistic and inference models."@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyTitle "K. Murphy. Machine learning: A probabilistic perspective. 2012"@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyType "Bibliografía"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/2> a ns1:DidacticResource ;
    ns1:bibliographyDescription "Introduces the basics of using machine learning techniques in Python with Scikit-Learn and other tools."@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyTitle "A. Géron. Hands-On Machine Learning with Scikit-Learn, Keras & Tensor Flow"@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyType "Bibliografía"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/3> a ns1:DidacticResource ;
    ns1:bibliographyDescription "The basic reference for Deep Learning models."@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyTitle "W. Goodfellow, J. Bengio and A. Courville, Deep Learning, 2016, HTML version available in: http://www.deeplearningbook.org/."@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyType "Bibliografía"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/4> a ns1:DidacticResource ;
    ns1:bibliographyDescription "It presents some fundamentals of statistical learning, and illustrates them with applications developed in R."@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyTitle "G. James, D. Witten, T. Hastie, R. Tibshirani, An Introduction to Statistical Learning, with applications in R, Springer Verlag, Berlin Heidelberg, 2014."@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyType "Bibliografía"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/5> a ns1:DidacticResource ;
    ns1:bibliographyDescription "It presents with rigor and extension the mathematical foundations (especially the probabilistic ones) of different models to address machine learning problems."@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyTitle "C. Bishop, Pattern Recognition and Machine Learning, Springer 2006."@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyType "Bibliografía"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/303000088/2025-26/didactic_resource/6> a ns1:DidacticResource ;
    ns1:bibliographyDescription "It presents the fundamentals of machine learning using neural network models."@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyTitle "S. Haykin, Neural Networks and Learning Machines, Prentice Hall, 2008."@es ;
    ns1:bibliographyType "Bibliografía"@es .

